      "slide_or_page": 35,
      "element_type": "text_box",
      "element_id": "slide_35_TextBox_11",
      "source_text": "The requirement may be defined in the form of:\nPerformance or technical specifications; draft service level agreements\nDraft contracts and KPIs\nA statement of source requirements (SSR), describing the requirement (specifically for the purposes of market testing)",
      "character_count": 262,
